data.description: Discover a unique opportunity in the heart of the Pottstown School District! This distinctive residential single home has plenty of space as a single family home but also presents the ideal canvas for a duplex transformation, offering endless potential for investment or multi-generational living if desired. With its charming brick facade and two separate entrances, this property opens the door to creativity and versatility. The home has 4 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms on the 2nd floor as well as a large finished area on the 3rd floor that could serve many different uses.  Considering this property as an investment? The bedrooms can easily be divided making each unit 2 bedrooms and 1 full bathroom, each with its own kitchen. Hardwood floors throughout add a touch of timeless elegance to the interior. The basement is private for each unit/side. This is more than a residence; it's an investment in your future. Whether you're seeking a spacious single-family dwelling or envisioning the potential of a duplex gem, this property is perfect for your unique vision. There are 2 wall heater units that use natural gas which has been disconnected.  Built in AC units are inoperative. Seller is looking to sell as-is. For added peace of mind, the seller is offering a one-year America's Preferred Home Warranty! Schedule your showing today!
